name: ibuprofen
indications: Uses • temporarily relieves minor aches and pains due to: • minor pain of arthritis • muscular aches • backache • menstrual cramps • headache • toothache • the common cold • temporarily reduces fever
warnings: Warnings Allergy alert: Naproxen sodium may cause a severe allergic reaction, especially in people allergic to aspirin. Symptoms may include: • hives • facial swelling • asthma (wheezing) • shock • sk
dosage: Directions • do not take more than directed • the smallest effective dose should be used • drink a full glass of water with each dose • if taken with food, this product may take longer to work adults
